    "base_path":  "/guidance/apply-for-a-certificate-of-fitness-for-call-to-the-bar-of-northern-ireland-or-a-certificate-of-pupillage-for-scotland",
    "content_id":  "5d2c995c-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef",
    "description":  "Guide for barristers asking the Law Officers for permission to join the Bar of Northern Ireland or the Faculty of Advocates in Scotland.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eOne of the functions of the Law Officers (the Attorney General and Solicitor General) is to approve applications from members of the Bar of England and Wales who need a certificate in order to be called to the Bar of Northern Ireland, or who want to apply for membership of the Faculty of Advocates in Scotland.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"apply-for-a-certificate-to-be-called-to-the-bar-of-northern-ireland\"\u003eApply for a certificate to be called to the Bar of Northern Ireland\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"what-to-submit\"\u003eWhat to submit:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003col\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eA short letter addressed to the Law Officers requesting a certificate of fitness for call to the Bar of Northern Ireland and stating why you are seeking call and whether it is temporary or permanent\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eA copy of your Practising Certificate\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eA brief curriculum vitae showing the nature of your practice\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eReferences as to your suitability for the Northern Ireland Bar\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"apply-for-certificates-of-pupillage-for-scotland\"\u003eApply for Certificates of Pupillage for Scotland\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"what-to-submit-1\"\u003eWhat to submit:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003col\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eA short letter addressed to the Law Officers requesting a certificate and why you are seeking call\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eYour completion of pupillage certificate\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eYour curriculum vitae\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eYour Bar Standards Board certificate\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-submit-your-application\"\u003eHow to submit your application\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eplease send to: \u003ca href=\"mailto:correspondence@attorneygeneral.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ecorrespondence@attorneygeneral.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eor:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAttorney General’s Office\n\u003cbr\u003e102 Petty France\n\u003cbr\u003eLondon\n\u003cbr\u003eSW1H 9EA\n\u003cbr\u003eUnited Kingdom\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
